'''Centro Juventud Sionista''', or simply '''Sionista''', is a [[basketball]] club based in [[Paraná, Entre Ríos|Paraná]], [[Argentina]]. The team currently plays in the [[Liga Nacional de Básquet]] (LNB), using the Estadio Moisés Flesler as its home arena.

