The '''Stadium of Ksar''' is a sports field in northeastern [[Nouakchott]], Mauritania. It is located to the northeast of the [[Presidential Palace (Mauritania)|Presidential Palace]], near the [[Old Fort, Nouakchott|Old Fort]] and College d'Applicatio.<ref name="GM">{{cite map|title=[[Google Maps]]|publisher=Google|accessdate=10 March 2011}}</ref>

